##### Quarter-finals

*   **18 March (D/N):** [South Africa](/South_Africa_national_cricket_team) (134/1) defeated [Sri Lanka](/Sri_Lanka_national_cricket_team) (133) by 9 wickets at [Sydney Cricket Ground](/Sydney_Cricket_Ground), [Sydney](/Sydney).
*   **19 March (D/N):** [India](/India_national_cricket_team) (302/6) defeated [Bangladesh](/Bangladesh_national_cricket_team) (193) by 109 runs at [Melbourne Cricket Ground](/Melbourne_Cricket_Ground), [Melbourne](/Melbourne).
*   **20 March (D/N):** [Australia](/Australia_national_cricket_team) (216/4) defeated [Pakistan](/Pakistan_national_cricket_team) (213) by 6 wickets at [Adelaide Oval](/Adelaide_Oval), [Adelaide](/Adelaide).
*   **21 March (D/N):** [New Zealand](/New_Zealand_national_cricket_team) (393/6) defeated [West Indies](/West_Indies_cricket_team) (250) by 143 runs at [Wellington Regional Stadium](/Wellington_Regional_Stadium), [Wellington](/Wellington).

##### Semi-finals

*   **24 March (D/N):** [New Zealand](/New_Zealand_national_cricket_team) (299/6) defeated [South Africa](/South_Africa_national_cricket_team) (281/5) by 4 wickets ([D/L method](/D/L_method)) at [Eden Park](/Eden_Park), [Auckland](/Auckland).
*   **26 March (D/N):** [Australia](/Australia_national_cricket_team) (328/7) defeated [India](/India_national_cricket_team) (233) by 95 runs at [Sydney Cricket Ground](/Sydney_Cricket_Ground), [Sydney](/Sydney).

### Final

The grand culmination of the [2015 Cricket World Cup](/2015_Cricket_World_Cup) was the final match, a high-stakes encounter that determined the ultimate champion of the tournament.

*   **29 March (D/N):** [Australia](/Australia_national_cricket_team) (186/3) defeated [New Zealand](/New_Zealand_national_cricket_team) (183) by 7 wickets at [Melbourne Cricket Ground](/Melbourne_Cricket_Ground), [Melbourne](/Melbourne).

